        <p> There are certain device requirements to run Explorer, as well as requirements on the data that is used within the app.</p>


        <h3>Data requirements</h3>
        <p>To use your maps in Explorer, you must have an ArcGIS organizational account. Your maps can include data from ArcGIS Online, Portal for ArcGIS, and ArcGIS for Server.</p>


